"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640365087,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"XsZC9ElqQPUZiNmdxyrC-UwqWqZsBQ1TyTsnWJ_6rjM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x52466898A1B2280284610E7b741A72c21C2Bb536\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RfOZKrJRlBHpOoADoTO7_izcL7Rop_9UJaNBCBBGWhA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F5RZOwQ2S6IKA5xd-jp0VNFZbSA14rraNQqkvSnoPkM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"DRjzrZuxQVyGpST_nc67tcdOQUcYHFHXCL_6dbPdNTmTy4WWgnSWW-mJflrAWGPl7V6lQ5asd_O8sajAegAdZA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x12ebbfccdc4348afa259b6ae1c762ad9b92b24712a94d5be4efceb5b98bc713e4560497a7903fcb86be6ef9b9ed6f885e2987d3c3cbe0f140f892379054590bc1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RfOZKrJRlBHpOoADoTO7_izcL7Rop_9UJaNBCBBGWhA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F5RZOwQ2S6IKA5xd-jp0VNFZbSA14rraNQqkvSnoPkM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi